-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                  KNOWN BUGS                                   
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

GR artifacts not completely accurate
	seems to be immune to offset fragmentation in hardware tests
Right horizontal scan line not matching up in 40-col modes
Speaker static at startup
Does not successfully pass IIe memory test
Needs to reset keyboard when focus is regained to avoid stuck-keys


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                 VERSION INFO                                   
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

CPU with accurate cycle timing, synced with emulated monitor refresh rate
	decimal mode incomplete
Memory bus
	missing paddle
	missing cassette switches or stand-ins
	need to swap outputs from video to keyboard out for 16 read types
Text / graphics modes with accurate color and pixel offset
Key input matches IIe behavior and timing
Shift-insert or shift-F2 pastes contents of clipboard (can be cancelled with ctrl-reset or F12)
Sound physics implemented
